{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">About the game</h2>Zakon is an arcade-flight game with an emphasis on fighting big monsters in a soviet futuristic-punk city. Every action that you take directly affects your social score, the better citizen you are, the higher your social score you have.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918120/extras/fast_gif.gif?t=1738272024\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">GLORY TO THE MOTHERLAND</h2>Dear soldier, <br><br>Because of your recent achievements against rebels, your social score is high enough to give you the opportunity to be the first pilot of our new combat jet for special operations within Molegrad.<br><br>Your duties, however, will not change. You have to keep the motherland safe and free from rebels, just like in the simulation.<br><br>Keep your social score high, spread the VOZD's voice across Krasnogorie, and do not even think about committing anti-state actions and falling into their propaganda, like your predecessors.  Doing so will cause your social credit to decrease immediately and you will be considered an enemy of the motherland.<br><br><u>VOZD - FATHER<br><br>MOTHERLAND - MOTHER</u><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918120/extras/busik_gif.gif?t=1738272024\" /><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight big monsters in a high-density city<br></li><li>Increase your social score to become a respected citizen and to get all benefits.<br></li><li>Spread the VOZD's voice across Molegrad<br></li><li>Eliminate any protests and rebellions in order to maintain power.<br></li><li>Find all upgrades<br></li><li>Retro PS1 inspired graphics</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1918120/extras/monster_opt_opt.gif?t=1738272024\" />","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackgroun